WEBVTT

00:00:00.800 --> 00:00:07.200
ACTION: Lumen Atlas boots from a corrupted city ledger.
The first key will decide which myths wake next.

00:00:08.200 --> 00:00:17.400
ACTION: In Central Plaza, YOU meet NEGO-CHAN.
NEGO-CHAN: The Atlas is blinking. Bring back the first Lumen Key.

00:00:18.200 --> 00:00:27.400
ACTION: Cross Glitch Route 01 before the map rewrites itself.
NEON: I will mark the safe tiles. Keep moving.

00:00:28.200 --> 00:00:37.400
ACTION: At Golden Temple, KANE-KAMI reveals the Vault attack.
KANE-KAMI: Find ZERO and patch the gate.

00:00:38.200 --> 00:00:47.400
ACTION: ZERO patches Data Causeway while hostile signals close in.
ZERO: Hold the line. I can open one clean route.

00:00:48.200 --> 00:00:57.400
ACTION: Choose a negotiation stance: Read, Push, or Build Trust.
YOU: Build trust. We need allies, not just money.

00:00:58.200 --> 00:01:07.400
ACTION: Enter Underground Vault and recover the first Lumen Key.
SYSTEM: Key signature found. Extraction window is collapsing.

00:01:08.200 --> 00:01:19.000
ACTION: Return the key. The Oracle Gate begins to open.
ORACLE: One key lights eight regions. Seven shadows answer.

00:01:20.200 --> 00:01:26.600
MIDGAME PREVIEW: Guilds, labs, bridges, and the Eye-Void awaken.
NEXT: Routes unlock, allies clash, and the city chooses a keeper.

00:01:26.800 --> 00:01:29.600
PLAY NOW: NEON MYTHOS: Lumen Atlas
